<varlistentry>
    <term>Assembly Manual</term>
    <listitem>
        <para>This document defines the Shuttleworth Foundation specification for manufacture of a
            production Freedom Toaster system. It explains how to assemble the physical housing and
            computer equipment that comprise a Freedom Toaster, it also provides the specifications
            and instructions required in order to make those parts that are bespoke and cannot be
            bought from a supply-store.</para>
    </listitem>
</varlistentry>
